    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"rest completely\"... that's a pretty heavy way to put it. what does that actually look like? because it feels like the only way to actually stop the performance is to just stop everything. like, if there's nothing left to be, why keep doing this?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
